snippet.title: Snacko - A Farming Cat-venture 🌱 Coming to Switch & PC 2022
snippet.description:
💌 Get notified of our Switch Launch: https://www.snacko.land/switch
🎮 Wishlist us on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1125510/Snacko

🐾 About Snacko 🐾
Lift a curse and revitalized a ruined island in Snacko, where former big city kitties Momo and Mikan are starting a new life! Grow crops, raise fluffy cows, go fishing, exploring, customize and decorate as you please, and much, much more in this farming cat-venture.

✨ Socials ✨
📌 Website: http://snacko.land​
📌 Discord: http://discord.gg/snackodev​
📌 Twitter: https://twitter.com/snackodev​
